Which of the following are theorems of K?

1. $(\Box A \vee \Box B) \rightarrow \Box(A \vee B)$
2. $(\Box A \wedge \Diamond B) \rightarrow \Diamond(A \wedge B)$
3. $\Box (A \wedge \Diamond B) \rightarrow \Diamond(A \wedge B)$
4. $(\Box A \rightarrow \Box B) \rightarrow (\Diamond A \rightarrow \Diamond B)$
5. $\Box (A \rightarrow B) \rightarrow (\Diamond A \rightarrow \Diamond B)$
